reviewText: Bought this for my son who LOVES car racing and demolition derbies. He was so bored with it, it's just classical music all the way through.  Can't hear the cars or crashes. Definitely not worth the buy.

Purchased this for a nephew who loves car crashes.  The audio has background semi classical music.  Russian language is used.  No sound of car to car contact, tire squealing, brakes, etc.  Very disappointed.
